"    </p>",
"    <p class=\"headingAnchor2\" id=\"H1193301\">",
"     <span class=\"h2\">",
"      Patient level information",
"     </span>",
"     &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;UpToDate offers two types of patient education materials.",
"    </p>",
"    <p class=\"headingAnchor2\" id=\"H1193316\">",
"     <span class=\"h3\">",
"      The Basics",
"     </span>",
